# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# FRONTEND ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Application ────────────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_NAME=SocialHub
REACT_APP_VERSION=1.0.0
NODE_ENV=development

# ── API Configuration ─────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:3000
REACT_APP_API_TIMEOUT=15000

# ── Authentication ────────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_JWT_EXPIRY=3600
REACT_APP_REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRY=604800

# ── OAuth Providers ───────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret_here
REACT_APP_FACEBOOK_APP_ID=your_facebook_app_id_here
REACT_APP_FACEBOOK_APP_SECRET=your_facebook_app_secret_here
REACT_APP_LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID=your_linkedin_client_id_here
REACT_APP_LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET=your_linkedin_client_secret_here

# ── Social Media APIs ──────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_instagram_token_here
REACT_APP_TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN=your_twitter_token_here
REACT_APP_FACEBOOK_PAGE_TOKEN=your_facebook_page_token_here
REACT_APP_LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_linkedin_token_here

# ── Storage ────────────────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_STORAGE_TYPE=local  # 'local', 's3', 'gcs'
REACT_APP_S3_BUCKET=your_s3_bucket
REACT_APP_S3_REGION=ap-southeast-1

# ── Analytics ──────────────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_GOOGLE_ANALYTICS_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
REACT_APP_SENTRY_DSN=https://your_sentry_dsn_here

# ── Feature Flags ──────────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_ENABLE_2FA=true
REACT_APP_ENABLE_COLLAB=true
REACT_APP_ENABLE_AI_HUB=true
REACT_APP_ENABLE_SOCIAL_LISTENING=false
REACT_APP_ENABLE_INFLUENCER_DISCOVERY=false

# ── URLs ───────────────────────────────────────────
REACT_APP_FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3001
REACT_APP_DOCS_URL=https://docs.socialhub.app
REACT_APP_SUPPORT_URL=https://support.socialhub.app
